products.title: Zambezi 25mm Tawny Real Wood Perfect Fit Blind
products.description: As a warm medium brown wood stain, this zambezi tawny perfect fit blind is practical and oh-so stylish. Wooden shades can be used to pull the room together through co-ordinating floors and furnishing. A softer look on painted slats, this perfect fit wooden blind adds a homey, traditional finish. Using and easy clip-on fitting system, this perfect fit wooden blind is both drill and screw-free, and provides a child-safe option for your upvc windows or doors.
